modules.description: This module performs asynchronous DNS resolution using custom communication functions for sending and receiving DNS packets. It supports standard DNS queries and DNSSEC validation, operating on DNS packet structures and domain names. It is used to resolve hostnames to IP addresses in asynchronous network applications.

This module provides asynchronous DNS resolution using functions like `gethostbyname` to query IP addresses from hostnames. It works with Unix-specific networking interfaces and handles DNS packets using the `Dns.Packet` module's types. Use it to perform non-blocking DNS lookups in networked applications like web clients or distributed systems.
